@startuml
object Teacher
object "Auth API" as AuthAPI
object "Teacher Discord verification" as TeacherDiscordVerification
object "Discord bot credential" as DiscordBotCredential
object "Teacher storage" as TeacherStorage
object "Discord OAuth" as DiscordOAuth
Teacher --> AuthAPI : 1: request/link callback
AuthAPI --> TeacherDiscordVerification : 2: build/handle
TeacherDiscordVerification --> DiscordBotCredential : 3: load client credential
TeacherDiscordVerification --> DiscordOAuth : 4: exchange code
TeacherDiscordVerification --> DiscordOAuth : 5: fetch user
TeacherDiscordVerification --> TeacherStorage : 6: load teacher
TeacherDiscordVerification --> TeacherStorage : 7: save Teacher Discord identity
TeacherDiscordVerification --> AuthAPI : 8: redirect url
AuthAPI --> Teacher : 9: redirect
@enduml
